                    Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting isum has been the industry's standard dummy te ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer.
                  </div>
                </div>
                <!-- End Single Method -->
              </div>
              <!-- End Payment Method -->
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

